* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Thutmose III (Deir el-Bahari)|de|Totentempel des Thutmosis III. (Deir el-Bahari)|ja|トトメス3世葬祭殿|zh|图特摩斯三世葬祭殿}}

*Million‑year houses at {{ill|Qurna|de|el-Qurna|ja|エル・クルナ|zh|古尔纳}}*
* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Seti I (Qurna)|de|Totentempel des Sethos I. (Qurna)|ja|セティ1世葬祭殿 (クルナ)|zh|塞提一世葬祭殿}}
* {{ill|Temple of the Ramesside kings (Asasif)|de|Tempel der Ramessiden (Asasif)|ja|ラメシデ朝神殿 (アサシフ)|zh|拉美西德王神庙}}
* Temple of {{ill|Thutmose III|de|Thutmosis III.|ja|トトメス3世|zh|图特摩斯三世}} (el‑Qurna)
* Temple of {{ill|Ramesses Siptah|de|Siptah|ja|シプター|zh|西普塔赫}}
* Temple of {{ill|Amenhotep II|de|Amenophis II.|ja|アメンホテプ2世|zh|阿蒙霍特普二世}}
* The {{ill|Ramesseum|de|Ramesseum|ja|ラムセウム|zh|拉美西乌姆}} (temple of Ramesses II)
* Temple of {{ill|Thutmose IV|de|Thutmosis IV.|ja|トトメス4世|zh|图特摩斯四世}}
* Temple of {{ill|Twosret|de|Tausret|ja|トゥオスレト|zh|图斯雷特}}
* Temple of {{ill|Merneptah|de|Merenptah|ja|メルエンプタハ|zh|麦伦普塔赫}}
* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Amenhotep III|de|Tempel des Amenophis III.|ja|アメンホテプ3世葬祭殿|zh|阿蒙霍特普三世葬祭殿}} (behind the Colossi of Memnon)
* Temple of {{ill|Ramesses IV|de|Ramses IV.|ja|ラムセス4世|zh|拉美西斯四世}}
* Temple of {{ill|Thutmose II|de|Thutmosis II.|ja|トトメス2世|zh|图特摩斯二世}}
* Temple of {{ill|Horemheb|de|Haremhab|ja|ホルエムヘブ|zh|霍伦海布}}, {{ill|Ay|de|Eje|ja|アイ|zh|阿伊}}, and {{ill|Tutankhamun|de|Tutanchamun|ja|ツタンカーメン|zh|图坦卡蒙}}
* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Ramesses III|de|Totentempel des Ramses III.|ja|ラムセス3世葬祭殿|zh|拉美西斯三世葬祭殿}} ({{ill|Medinet Habu|de|Medinet Habu|ja|メディネト・ハブ|zh|马迪纳特哈布}})

=== Abydos ===
* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Ramesses II (Abydos)|de|Tempel des Ramses II. von Abydos|ja|ラムセス2世葬祭殿 (アビドス)|zh|拉美西斯二世葬祭殿 (阿比多斯)}}
* {{ill|Mortuary Temple of Seti I (Abydos)|de|Totentempel des Sethos I. (Abydos)|ja|セティ1世葬祭殿 (アビドス)|zh|塞提一世葬祭殿 (阿比多斯)}}: *Hut‑abdu‑Men‑maat‑Ra* (Ḥwt‑3bḏw‑mn‑mȝʿ.t‑Rʿ) – “House of Men‑maat‑Ra in Abydos”

