|NAME                = <hiero>O6-X1:O1-N35:X1-C11-Z3-G17-M4-M4-M4</hiero><br/>Hut‑net‑hehu‑em‑renput<br/>''Ḥw.t‑n.t‑ḥḥw‑m‑rnp.wt''<br/>“House of Millions of Years”
